CutefishOS Repository

    GitHub CutefishOS Repository at https://github.com/linuxcutefish/packages

    How to add a repository:

    curl -s --compressed "https://linuxcutefish.github.io/packages/cutefishos.gpg" | gpg --dearmor | sudo tee /etc/apt/trusted.gpg.d/cutefishos.gpg >/dev/null  
sudo curl -s --compressed -o /etc/apt/sources.list.d/cutefishos.list "https://linuxcutefish.github.io/packages/cutefishos.list"  
sudo apt update

    About:

    CutefishOS is an elegant, beautiful and easy-to-use Linux desktop operating system. It runs Cutefish Desktop has a modern style design. Our goal is to provide users with a comfortable interface design, better user experience and a better choice.
